  "_doc": "Kamigawa: Neon Dynasty (NEO) booster recipe. The `draft` block is generated by scripts/gen-booster-contents.mjs from data/_collation-facts/neo.json (source: The Collation Project, lethe.xyz/mtg/collation) — do not hand-edit it unless you also remove its facts source. The `collector` block is hand-authored from Wizards' official \"Collecting Kamigawa: Neon Dynasty\" article (magic.wizards.com/en/news/feature/collecting-kamigawa-neon-dynasty-2022-01-27) and the matching Product Overview; the 15-card + token slot structure is verbatim from the Product Overview. NEO is a 2022 set (pre-Play Booster) so there is NO play booster. Booster Fun in NEO: extended-art, borderless, Ninja/Samurai showcase, soft-glow showcase (Scryfall frame_effects showcase), foil-etched (Scryfall finishes etched), and the neon-ink Hidetsugu (Scryfall promo_types neonink — the only neon-ink card, blue/green/red/Phyrexian ink at roughly 8:4:1 weighting per the article). The foil 'ukiyo-e land' slot is the full-art land — modeled as full-art basics plus the five legendary channel lands. Commander rares/mythics come from the Neon Dynasty Commander set (nec). Set composition: 107C / 88U / 59R / 18M. 'authoritative' so the date heuristic doesn't fabricate a play booster. AUDIT 2026-06: special-finish outcome rarities corrected to match the actual printed sheets (pool-verified): neon_ink->rare.",
